verbose_text: The proportion of N derived from atmosphere (% Ndfa) and amount of N 2 -fixed for both legumes were calculated as follows :% Ndfa = (delta 15 N ref-delta 15 N leg)/(delta 15 N ref-B) x 100Where delta 15 N ref and delta 15 N leg are the 15 N natural abundance (/1000) in the non fixing reference crops (maize for this study) and the fixing species.
